data.title: Army ManTech
data.meta_description: The U.S. Army Manufacturing Technology (ManTech) Program is an industrial preparedness program focused on addressing Army-wide manufacturing requirements across the specific systems and platforms. For more information visit: https://www.dodmantech.mil
data.text:
The U.S. Army Manufacturing Technology (ManTech) Program is an industrial preparedness program focused on addressing Army-wide manufacturing requirements across the following systems and platforms:

Network, Command Control, Communications, and Intelligence

Ground

Aviation

Soldiers

Weapons
